and today we're going to be talking about

00:00:05.050 --> 00:00:14.269
the Musty Lite Rider. This is actually a pretty
snazzy stroller. Kind of comparable to the

00:00:14.269 --> 00:00:22.600
Stokke Xplory to a certain degree. If you
notice, this particular stroller, it comes

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:28.390
with a bassinet and it comes with the older
kids seat, which I will show you. If you notice,

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:34.510
the bassinet is nice and high. You don't have
to do a lot of bending over to reach your

00:00:34.510 --> 00:00:40.309
kid. It makes it a lot easier for you to interact
with your baby. That's what I meant by sort

00:00:40.309 --> 00:00:47.510
of somewhat like the Stokke Xplory. Nice height
adjustable handle, which makes it very easy

00:00:47.510 --> 00:00:56.739
to adjust for your comfort. Bassinet comes
with the canopy. You can pop this unit out

00:00:56.739 --> 00:01:05.070
of the base. Simply popping there, picking
up, set it to the side. You use your bassinet

00:01:05.070 --> 00:01:12.920
